data.description: Madison Place premieres this 3 Bed 2.5 Bath Townhouse, bursting with possibilities! Great opportunity for you to finish off this townhome and make it your own! Light & bright Living Room welcomes you in featuring, crown molding, ceramic tile flooring, and recessed lighting. Formal Dining Room is perfect for hosting dinner guests. The Eat-in Kitchen offers SS Appliances, Quartz Counter, & Pantry. Unwind in the Family Room featuring a wood burning fireplace. 1/2 Bath completes this main floor. Upstairs, the main Full Bath with tub shower + 3 generously sized Bedrooms with NEW Luxe Vinyl Plank Flooring. Master Suite boasts it's own private ensuite bath with tiled stall shower. In unit laundry is so convenient! Relax outdoors on the quaint patio. Close to area shopping, dining, & major roads for an easy commute. Come & see TODAY!
